{"tid":428843,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先可以連跑幾個圈","createTime":"2017-10-08T11:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T02:03:27.000Z","uid":90663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd6cc44f020f245f2299754d499fa8dc72b77d5","tid":428843,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"近排開始跑步，上次有朋友陪所以可以連跑5個圈<br />\n<br />\n但今次自己去，連續跑左兩個圈就攰到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己一個跑步嘅你地，有咩方法係可以堅持跑咁多個圈？<br />\n<br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2219257b3fe4cece8bff61d488203f5c9128d8","tid":428843,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"聽住歌跑"},{"pid":"11415d1d1ea5bef7bfdfff613f7a7c57e99ef315","tid":428843,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽住歌跑</blockquote><br />\n條線hi晒啲汗唔會覺得好核突？痴住晒咁"},{"pid":"e042925beceab7007b6bd0470cd62d27ee2a9198","tid":428843,"uid":42527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽住歌跑</blockquote><br />\n條線hi晒啲汗唔會覺得好核突？痴住晒咁</blockquote><br />\n做運動緊係用無線耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb74513b1e5dd95dfe5b701bc4c33e73a79008","tid":428843,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"慢慢跑啦有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6d1cbaed2b1fbf484ebf6a92cff0ba8f5981cb","tid":428843,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"控制速度 唔係越快越勁 要留氣<br />\n一開頭第一個星期可能最多跑1km 然後慢慢操 第2星期1.2k 1.5k ..咁慢慢就會升到（開頭）<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"561b0996fc6c946ae38d9a0deca437fca3b47e4f","tid":428843,"uid":127553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T19:06:44.000Z","msg":"呼吸好緊要<br />\n我就用鼻吸口呼，配合步速<br />\n吸呼呼，吸呼呼 咁樣"},{"pid":"eef0723958ec1e286b5f925027d6fbe1adeccdb6","tid":428843,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T19:09:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37437e59993acc41f7a566f8cfdf6be76c1fad4d","tid":428843,"uid":127439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"慢慢咁跑<br />\n以前我跑5分鐘就會喘要停低慢行1-2分鐘先再跑到<br />\n最近改變方法將個速度再減慢啲就可以連住跑到30分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練到咁上下可以逐漸逐漸加返快個速度"},{"pid":"f9acf9e550268e8c598113f5a421b0dc94cb6902","tid":428843,"uid":44808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"鼻吸口呼,兩吸一呼,<br />\n唔好用力跑,要好似輕放隻腳掌落地咁<br />\n唔好跑太快"}]}